           move      spaces               to   w-cnt-sts-vis-key
                                               w-cnt-sts-vis-tes
                                               w-cnt-sts-vis-pte
                                               w-cnt-sts-vis-cor
                                               w-cnt-sts-vis-rig
                                               w-cnt-sts-vis-pie
                                               w-cnt-sts-vis-ppi      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione area di controllo variazioni    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-cnt-var-tes-cor      .
