      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-num-prt-000      thru pmt-num-prt-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Data registrazione                          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-dat-reg-000      thru pmt-dat-reg-999        .
