           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione prompts per numero protocollo             *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       pmt-num-prt-000.
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      20                   to   v-car                  .
           move      04                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "Numero protocollo  :"
                                          to   v-alf                  .
