      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione prompts per data registrazione            *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       pmt-dat-reg-000.
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      20                   to   v-car                  .
           move      04                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      52                   to   v-pos                  .
